g.text: This workflow illustrates how to blend different data sources whithin KNIME Analytics Platform. A Java Script node is used to visualize average age vs. product in the resulting blended table.
Blend together many different data sources through an effective ETL (Extract, Transform and Loading).
http://www.knime.org/learning-hub contains useful links, e.g. tutorials, videos, books, slides, etc ... for each kind of data analytics topic.
The files are located in TheData/Misc/
- Concatenate web activity data from old and new systems
- Replace sentiment texts with numeric scores
- Set all product names to lowercase
- Join all data together by the customerKey column
- Group by products, and aggregate by age (mean)
Create a bar chart showing the average age of customers for
